headline: Banks have a busy week: Fed decision, Goldman conference, & more
summary: It's an important week for banks and the financial sector (XLF), from the Federal Reserve's interest rate decision to Goldman Sachs's (GS) industry conference. Yahoo Finance Senior Reporter David Hollerith joins Market Domination Overtime host Josh Lipton to outline what's in store for the sector this week. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime.

headline: Medline aiming to raise $5.37 billion in biggest US IPO this year
summary: Investing.com -- Healthcare manufacturing giant Medline has filed for a 179,000,000 share IPO on the Nasdaq Global Select Market, with a price range of $26-$30 per share, potentially raising up to $5.37 billion in what would be the largest US initial public offering of 2025.
